=20

Dear I.C.,

=20

After a more in depth review of our ICDs for the Denver CDS system, a =
typo has been noted in two documents, specifically the Communications =
ICD (DDN-0432-0091) and the CCTV ICD (DDN-0432-0097) as was highlighted =
by Minseong Jeon last week:

=20

cid:image004.png@01D2887B.CA4C03E0

=20

All ICDs for the Denver CDS system should use the 0x0803 selector on =
both A and B car for the TimeStamp variable. We have updated both =
erroneous ICDs (attached and available on the Client Access Site). The =
impact of this change is that both the Comm and CCTV subsystems will =
likely require a minor software update in order to facilitate a =
functional TimeStamp synchronization between all subsystems.

=20

Please let me know if you have any questions.=20

=20

Thank you,

