PROP node, Network Variable #3 : selector =3D 0x0803, data: 0000/00/00 =
00:00:00

FBCU node, Network Variable #3 : selector =3D 0x0803, data: 0000/00/00 =
00:00:00

APU node, Network Variable #3 : selector =3D 0x0803, data: 0000/00/00 =
00:00:00

HVAC-A node Network Variable #3 : selector =3D 0x0803, data: FFFF/00/00 =
00:00:00 (FFFF is put by the TCU itself to indicate no valid time stamp)

HVAC-F node Network Variable #3 : selector =3D 0x0803, data: FFFF/00/00 =
00:00:00 (FFFF is put by the TCU itself to indicate no valid time stamp)

=20

I do not know from here if it is the ICD document for the Communication =
system that have an error on it

